# docs/

Technical documentation for Intent covering methodology, rules library, agent systems, and extension architecture. Guides for authoring rules, implementing critics, and extending Intent via user plugins.

## Dirs

- `blog/` -- Intent methodology blog series exploring foundational philosophy through AI integration
- `blog-drafts/` -- Works-in-progress blog posts and narrative documentation
- `releases/` -- Archival release notes for Intent v1.2.1 through v2.9.0

## Files

- `rules.md` -- Rule library authoring guide with schema reference and examples
- `critics.md` -- Critic subagent contract, report format, and invocation patterns
- `writing-extensions.md` -- Extension authoring guide for ~/.intent/ext/ user customizations
